data.description: Incredible value for this luxury Summerlin home with 4 bedrooms+den+loft!  Come see why this property near highly desired private and public schools with MOUNTAIN, VALLEY, and STRIP views from the balcony can be yours.  Standout features include 3 Car Garage, Side Courtyard, Salt-Water Pool/spa, Lush Landscaping, Upgraded Wood-like Tile on main level, Quartz Countertops, Subway Tile, Stacking Sliding Glass Doors for Indoor/Outdoor living, Custom Sliding Barn Door, Covered Patio, Den/Study/Office, 2 Laundry Spaces, Outdoor Gas Fireplace, Stainless Steel Railing, Loft, and a Junior Suite Upstairs.  There are far more details to see in person. The Skystone community is near freeways, shopping, parks, hiking/running trails, and all things SUMMERLIN.  We invite you to come and see this dynamic property today.
